ess Improvement in Therapeutic Outcomes by Optimizing Pla" J Am Coll Cardiol 54 (2009): 678-85[5] "Product Information. Ticlid (ticlopidine)." Syntex Laboratories Inc, Palo Alto, CA.', 1767365203);
